## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all aspects of the issue due to the limited scope of the search. Additionally, the data is subject to publication bias, as studies with significant findings are more likely to be published. Further research, including longitudinal studies, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the long-term impacts of late-life divorce on women.